snippet.title: How to Become Better at Prioritization by fmr Dropbox PM
snippet.description:
A Product Management event in San Francisco on how to become a better at prioritization. 

👉 Subscribe here: http://bit.ly/2xMQLbS 
🕊️ Follow us on Twitter: http://bit.ly/2xAQklN 
💙 Like us on Facebook for free event tickets: http://bit.ly/2xPfjkh 
📷 Check us out on Instagram: http://bit.ly/2eHmfJp 

Find out more about us: https://prod.school/33hpEoA 💻

ABOUT US:
Founded in Silicon Valley in 2014, Product School is the global leader in product management training, with over 10,000 alumni, 20 campuses worldwide and a live online campus.

Product School’s certificates (PMC™,FPMC™,PLC™) are the most important industry-recognized certificates for product managers; and all of our instructors are senior-level product managers working at top technology companies such as Google, Facebook, Airbnb, PayPal, LinkedIn, and Netflix. See our upcoming courses here: https://prod.school/33hpEoA

In addition to classes, each of our campuses hosts weekly events with top industry professionals about Product Management, Data Analytics, Coding, Digital Marketing, UX Design and Product Leadership. Click here to see what we have coming up: https://prod.school/2pXC4Va

Product leaders from local top tech companies visit Product School campuses each week. Through lectures, panel discussions, and a variety of other forums, the world’s top product managers visit Product School to provide invaluable real-world insights into critical management issues. 

📓 The Product Book has arrived! Learn how to become a great Product Manager. Get your copy here: https://prod.school/33neWg8

#ProductManagement #ProductSchool #Upskill #TechEducation #Business #ProdMgmt #PMCertificate #ProductManager #Product #PM #IT #Management #PMP #ProductDesign #FinTech
